    <item>
      <title>战争恐慌引发债券热潮，科技股下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在央行做出重要决定之前，全球最大的科技公司遭遇抛售，导致股市下跌。地缘政治风险加剧，交易员纷纷寻求避险，债券和黄金价格上涨。油价持续走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 22:47:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迈阿密因办公空间问题借入 2.34 亿美元债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/miami-plans-to-borrow-243-million-for-troubled-office-building</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈阿密的租房成本已经变得如此之高，甚至连县政府都想成为自己的房东。为了实现这一目标，该县正在出售 2.34 亿美元的市政债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/miami-plans-to-borrow-243-million-for-troubled-office-building</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
